## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of recent data and the inherent variability in study designs and populations. Some studies may have conflicting results due to differences in methodology or sample size. Additionally, the long-term health impacts of non-nutritive sweeteners are still not fully understood, necessitating further research to draw more definitive conclusions.

